column14: All species abundances are in mg fwt/L  [fwt = freshweight]
The analysis in Benincˆ et al. (Nature 2008) covered all data from 16/06/1991 until 20/10/1997
The analysis in the Ecology Letters paper covers only the picophytoplankton, nanophytoplankton, calanoids copepods and rotifers, but over a longer time span from 12/07/1990 until 20/10/1997
Zero values are species abundances under the detection limit.
